    "title": {
        "rendered": "TinyMCE Enhanced Shortcodes"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "\n<p>It&#8217;s possible to parse shortcodes within the visual editor of TinyMCE and make them render actual content, rather than the shortcode itself.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Switching to the <code>Text</code> tab allows you to see the actual shortcode again.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Below are the built-in WordPress shortcodes that use this functionality.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Audio Shortcode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <code>[audio]</code> shortcode allows you to embed a single audio file.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1260\" height=\"318\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-01.png?resize=1260%2C318&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11237\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-01.png?w=1260&amp;ssl=1 1260w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-01.png?resize=300%2C75&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-01.png?resize=1024%2C258&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Caption Shortcode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <code>[caption]</code> shortcode wraps the image in a div and puts a <code>&lt;p class=\"wp-caption-text\"&gt;</code> tag around the caption.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"737\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-02.png?resize=737%2C502&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11239\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-02.png?w=737&amp;ssl=1 737w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-02.png?resize=300%2C204&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 737px) 100vw, 737px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Gallery Shortcode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <code>[gallery]</code> shortcode allows you to embed several images at once in a div.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1006\" height=\"912\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-03.png?resize=1006%2C912&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11236\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-03.png?w=1006&amp;ssl=1 1006w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-03.png?resize=300%2C271&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Playlist Shortcode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <code>[playlist]</code> shortcode allows you to attach more than one media file and render with an html5 playlist.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1272\" height=\"730\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-04.png?resize=1272%2C730&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11238\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-04.png?w=1272&amp;ssl=1 1272w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-04.png?resize=300%2C172&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-04.png?resize=1024%2C587&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Video Shortcode</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The <code>[video]</code> shortcode is very similar to the <code>[audio]</code> shortcode, it simply renders a video instead of audio.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1270\" height=\"940\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-05.png?resize=1270%2C940&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-11240\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-05.png?w=1270&amp;ssl=1 1270w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-05.png?resize=300%2C222&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/developer.wordpress.org/files/2014/09/shortcodes-tinymce-enhanced-shortcodes-05.png?resize=1024%2C757&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></figure></div>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
